{"tid":921910,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有白表單身申請者成功抽中首組號碼  其男友在現場大嚷","createTime":"2018-11-30T02:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T13:02:50.000Z","uid":19552,"like":250,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f597b86f492561135acbcdc15567942e03b590","tid":921910,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:58:54.000Z","msg":"新一期居屋項目抽籤結果今日（30日）正式出爐！攪珠期間，約數十名市民在樂富房委會中心「現場直擊」。有白表單身申請者成功抽中首組號碼，其男友在現場大嚷：「不可思議！」他又稱，晚上要回家大肆慶祝一番。<br />\n23歲鄭先生指出，其女友早前首次以單身人士身份入表，怎料今次卻成功首組號碼。他指出，一旦成功買樓，或會與女友一同入住及供樓。對於首次申請便成功「中籤」，他表示十分興奮，又說：「部電腦真係對我好！」他又說，今晚將會食飯慶祝，<span style=\"color: red;\">更會準備儲錢</span>。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，若日後可揀樓，會首選啟德啟朗苑，更強調不會選擇東涌裕泰苑。他更形容：「東涌比內地人攻陷咗！」然而，今期居屋白表單人申請數目達14.55萬宗，即使鄭先生的女友抽中首組號碼，亦只得約14%揀樓機會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2150247/org/64dd8b847b634350225fbdcd2d3c8d22.jpg/GUhv5IQ9Ue7JM-7VUnj280oIRzTW4t8NlNfQ45TX0OM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2150247%2Forg%2F64dd8b847b634350225fbdcd2d3c8d22.jpg%2FGUhv5IQ9Ue7JM-7VUnj280oIRzTW4t8NlNfQ45TX0OM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=9a34835b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f07bfb2c353bf6e9b8d55b99033655b6b8d4e85e","tid":921910,"uid":19552,"like":302,"dislike":5,"score":297,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:01:02.000Z","msg":"呢26萬份申請有幾多件係正常 仲話靠佢地做私樓向隅客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c04251652328c334c354b7832446dccc6aca84","tid":921910,"uid":144844,"like":133,"dislike":4,"score":129,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:02:20.000Z","msg":"單人有得唔揀東涌?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e8dd334405a5f9be138f022a6c27ed205636d8","tid":921910,"uid":90,"like":94,"dislike":3,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-1