:0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db45bc9c18d138fec1f5afab841d58ff1ee35b3b","tid":921910,"uid":124585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8f597b86f492561135acbcdc15567942e03b590","tid":921910,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:58:54.000Z","msg":"新一期居屋項目抽籤結果今日（30日）正式出爐！攪珠期間，約數十名市民在樂富房委會中心「現場直擊」。有白表單身申請者成功抽中首組號碼，其男友在現場大嚷：「不可思議！」他又稱，晚上要回家大肆慶祝一番。<br />\n23歲鄭先生指出，其女友早前首次以單身人士身份入表，怎料今次卻成功首組號碼。他指出，一旦成功買樓，或會與女友一同入住及供樓。對於首次申請便成功「中籤」，他表示十分興奮，又說：「部電腦真係對我好！」他又說，今晚將會食飯慶祝，<span style=\"color: red;\">更會準備儲錢</span>。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，若日後可揀樓，會首選啟德啟朗苑，更強調不會選擇東涌裕泰苑。他更形容：「東涌比內地人攻陷咗！」然而，今期居屋白表單人申請數目達14.55萬宗，即使鄭先生的女友抽中首組號碼，亦只得約14%揀樓機會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2150247/org/64dd8b847b634350225fbdcd2d3c8d22.jpg/GUhv5IQ9Ue7JM-7VUnj280oIRzTW4t8NlNfQ45TX0OM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2150247%2Forg%2F64dd8b847b634350225fbdcd2d3c8d22.jpg%2FGUhv5IQ9Ue7JM-7VUnj280oIRzTW4t8NlNfQ45TX0OM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=9a34835b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:49:22.000Z","msg":"23歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁後生就抽中, 好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2X尾, 3X嗰啲, 屎都無得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87edaddc067eed9482c95efbe65a11691786f28c","tid":921910,"uid":2923,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:51:53.000Z","msg":"當一個白痴既傻仔有少少自知之明,就唔會係現場做埋哂D柒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白單仲想揀最搶手既九龍區?東涌你都未必揀到靚單位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2